title: Teen Top Reveals Comeback Schedule For “HIGH FIVE”
text:
Display.Sharethrough.Soompi.1x1 
Teen Top is returning on April 10 with their second official album “HIGH FIVE”! 
On March 23, Teen Top revealed a teaser schedule for their upcoming comeback. After releasing photo teasers and jacket images, they will drop their two music video teasers. For April 9, the schedule indicates “ANGEL,” which is the name of their fan club, but it is unclear what they have in store for us that day. Soompi.Display.News.English.300x250.BTF Soompi.Mobile.English.300x250.ATF 
Their album title “HIGH FIVE” symbolizes a new beginning for Teen Top with the five members C.A.P, Chunji, Niel, Ricky, and Changjo. In hindsight, this was the secret behind the spoiler image of them doing a high five, which was revealed on their official social media during a V Live broadcast .
